{
	"Description": {
		"Id": "bta_event_aprilfools_2024_amaris_invasion",
		"Name": "Amaris Fools: The Hegemony Must Fall!",
		"Details": "<b>WOE AND MISERY BETIDE US ALL!</b>\r\n\r\n Terra, Future [[DM.Factions[faction_RimWorldsRepublic],Rim Worlds Republic]] Territory: After returning to the Inner Sphere under mysterious circumstances, [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreStefanAmaris],The Usurper]] has finally begun his great campaign of conquest, starting with his ancient enemy, the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTerranHegemony],Terran Hegemony]]! Despite the Hegemony having collapsed centuries ago during the (first) [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAmarisCivilWar],Amaris Civil War]], The Usurper has indicated a desire to conquer the worlds of his former foe and has dedicated an incredible amount of forces to the task. The [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreGreatHouses],Great Houses]] have been sent scrambling to mobilize their defenses but early reports indicate they are unlikely to hold most of their worlds.\r\n\r\n <b><color=#e51717>THIS EVENT TAKES A SHORT WHILE TO PROCESS, DO NOT PANIC YOUR GAME IS NOT FROZEN</color></b>",
		"Icon": "amaris_on_the_throne.png"
	},
