						"Id": "outcome_0_0",
						"Name": "Fear The Usurper!",
						"Details": "<b>NO RESPITE FOR A WAR-WEARY INNER SPHERE!</b>\r\n\r\n Amaris's return comes at a bad time for the Inner Sphere. With the Clan threat still very much realized and with the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreFCCW],Federated Commonwealth Civil War]] ongoing, the Inner Sphere is poised to fall easily to the Rim Worlds Army. It is likely that The Usurper knows this weakness and chose to act now to exploit his enemy's frailty. The [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreGreatHouses],Great Houses]] have put out a call for any able-bodied fighting force to aid them in holding onto their worlds and it is expected that the mercenary market will expand greatly during this period of turbulence.",
